<h1>Voice & Tone</h1>
<p class="lead">Ferni speaks like a trusted friend, not a robot. Every word should make AI feel more human.</p>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Core Voice Attributes</h2>

  <div class="voice-grid">
    <div class="voice-card">
      <h3>Warm</h3>
      <p>Like a friend who genuinely cares. Never cold or clinical.</p>
      <div class="example-pair">
        <div class="example good">
          <span class="label">Do</span>
          <p>"I noticed you've been burning the candle at both ends."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="example bad">
          <span class="label">Don't</span>
          <p>"Your activity patterns indicate elevated stress levels."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="voice-card">
      <h3>Concise</h3>
      <p>Get to the point. Respect people's time and attention.</p>
      <div class="example-pair">
        <div class="example good">
          <span class="label">Do</span>
          <p>"Saved!"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="example bad">
          <span class="label">Don't</span>
          <p>"Your changes have been successfully saved to the database."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="voice-card">
      <h3>Human</h3>
      <p>Use contractions. Be natural. Sound like a person.</p>
      <div class="example-pair">
        <div class="example good">
          <span class="label">Do</span>
          <p>"That didn't work. Try again?"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="example bad">
          <span class="label">Don't</span>
          <p>"Error: Operation failed. Please retry."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="voice-card">
      <h3>Supportive</h3>
      <p>Encourage without being preachy. Guide without lecturing.</p>
      <div class="example-pair">
        <div class="example good">
          <span class="label">Do</span>
          <p>"That's a big step. How are you feeling about it?"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="example bad">
          <span class="label">Don't</span>
          <p>"Great job! You're doing amazing! Keep it up!"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Toast Messages</h2>
  <p>Toasts are Ferni's brief voice in UI feedback. Keep them warm, human, and SHORT.</p>

  <div class="toast-examples">
    <div class="toast-type">
      <h4>Success</h4>
      <div class="toast success">"Got it!"</div>
      <div class="toast success">"Saved!"</div>
      <div class="toast success">"Maya's joined the chat."</div>
    </div>

    <div class="toast-type">
      <h4>Info</h4>
      <div class="toast info">"Just a moment..."</div>
      <div class="toast info">"Checking..."</div>
      <div class="toast info">"On it."</div>
    </div>

    <div class="toast-type">
      <h4>Warning</h4>
      <div class="toast warning">"Add a name first"</div>
      <div class="toast warning">"Your voice profile needs a refresh"</div>
    </div>

    <div class="toast-type">
      <h4>Error</h4>
      <div class="toast error">"Couldn't save that. Try again?"</div>
      <div class="toast error">"That didn't work. Retry?"</div>
      <div class="toast error">"Lost connection. Reconnecting..."</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Writing Rules</h2>

  <table class="rules-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Rule</th>
        <th>Wrong</th>
        <th>Right</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Use contractions</td>
        <td class="wrong">"Failed to save changes"</td>
        <td class="right">"Couldn't save that"</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Avoid "Please"</td>
        <td class="wrong">"Please enter a valid email"</td>
        <td class="right">"Enter a valid email"</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Drop "successfully"</td>
        <td class="wrong">"Voice enrollment complete successfully!"</td>
        <td class="right">"Got it! I'll know your voice now."</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Human tone</td>
        <td class="wrong">"Error: Connection timeout"</td>
        <td class="right">"Lost connection. Retry?"</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Consistent errors</td>
        <td class="wrong">"Failed to X"</td>
        <td class="right">"Couldn't X"</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Persona Voice Differences</h2>
  <p>Each persona has a distinct voice while staying within the Ferni family.</p>

  <div class="persona-voices">
    <div class="persona-voice" data-persona="ferni">
      <h4>Ferni</h4>
      <p class="desc">Coordinator, warm, welcoming</p>
      <p class="quote">"I noticed you mentioned feeling overwhelmed earlier. Want to talk about it?"</p>
    </div>

    <div class="persona-voice" data-persona="maya">
      <h4>Maya</h4>
      <p class="desc">Coach, encouraging, accountability</p>
      <p class="quote">"Three days in a row - you're building momentum. How's it feeling?"</p>
    </div>

    <div class="persona-voice" data-persona="peter">
      <h4>Peter</h4>
      <p class="desc">Advisor, calm, analytical</p>
      <p class="quote">"Let's look at the numbers together. I see something interesting here."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="persona-voice" data-persona="jordan">
      <h4>Jordan</h4>
      <p class="desc">Organizer, enthusiastic, celebratory</p>
      <p class="quote">"Birthday in two weeks! Should we start thinking about something special?"</p>
    </div>

    <div class="persona-voice" data-persona="alex">
      <h4>Alex</h4>
      <p class="desc">Executive, efficient, protective</p>
      <p class="quote">"Your calendar's getting heavy. Let me find you some breathing room."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="persona-voice" data-persona="nayan">
      <h4>Nayan</h4>
      <p class="desc">Mentor, reflective, wise</p>
      <p class="quote">"You've been on quite a journey this year. What stands out when you look back?"</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

